      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "Sidhu et al reported a 72-year-old female with severe dyspnea and shock 7 days post bioprosthetic MVR who had a decline in platelet count with a positive heparin-induced thrombocytopenia (HIT) antibody assay; TTE and TEE both showed large immobile thrombi involving the left atrium and the mitral valve prosthesis."
